description:
Taylor, a junior in college, is as lean and in-shape as they come.

He is constantly exercising, and his trim, lean body certainly displays that. He doesn't hesitate to discuss how involved he is in sports. He doesn't stop.

After classes, he runs.After he runs, he plays basketball.And after basketball, he goes to the gym.Talk about energy. And we can only imagine what he's like in the bedroom... if you can handle the size of his cock.
title: Taylor
